name: Operación Fallida
overview: Yes indeed welcome to another game from Irongate aka Jojo, a game that doesn't just feature deadly enemies such as zombies, Nazi supermen and other creatures from outer space, but through the two levels of the game, you play as a soldier of the union that has discovered the entrance to an abandoned bunker from World War II; a bunker that was not long ago used as a base of operations experimenting with dangerous alien technology.
